<lb n="0475c22" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0475c2201" type="regular" style="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「以說此百八，<caesura/>寂靜祕密名，</l>
<lb n="0475c23" ed="T"/><l>能利諸有情。<caesura/>希有祕福田，</l>
<lb n="0475c24" ed="T"/><l>天上及人間，<caesura/>亦甚難逢遇，</l>
<lb n="0475c25" ed="T"/><l>令一切有情，<caesura/>瞻視得安樂。</l>
<lb n="0475c26" ed="T"/><l>智者應一心，<caesura/>澡浴淨其身，</l>
<pb n="0476a" ed="T" xml:id="T20.1106.0476a"/>
<lb n="0476a01" ed="T"/><l>三時專念誦，<caesura/>時彼人不久，</l>
<lb n="0476a02" ed="T"/><l>得王所愛敬，<caesura/>離苦得安樂，</l>
<lb n="0476a03" ed="T"/><l>貧者獲財寶，<caesura/>愚得大智慧，</l>
<lb n="0476a04" ed="T"/><l>聰睿不復疑，<caesura/>枷鎖得解脫，</l>
<lb n="0476a05" ed="T"/><l>不勝還得勝，<caesura/>冤<note n="0476001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">返＝反【明】</note><note n="0476001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">返【大】，反【明】</note><app n="0476001"><lem wit="【大】">返</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">反</rdg></app>為善<note n="0476002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">友＝支【元】</note><note n="0476002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">友【大】，支【元】</note><app n="0476002"><lem wit="【大】">友</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">支</rdg></app>。</l>
<lb n="0476a06" ed="T"/><l>鋒牙及利角，<caesura/>鬪諍并嶮難，</l>
<lb n="0476a07" ed="T"/><l>種種怖畏等，<caesura/>憶念此名者，</l>
<lb n="0476a08" ed="T"/><l>能救是諸怖，<caesura/>止息中<note n="0476003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天＝夭【宋】【明】</note><note n="0476003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天【大】，夭【宋】【明】</note><app n="0476003"><lem wit="【大】">天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】">夭</rdg></app>命，</l>
<lb n="0476a09" ed="T"/><l>名稱得廣布，<caesura/>恒生善貴族。</l>
<lb n="0476a10" ed="T"/><l>彼<note n="0476004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惟＝唯【宋】【元】</note><note n="0476004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惟【大】，唯【宋】【元】</note><app n="0476004"><lem wit="【大】">惟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">唯</rdg></app>獨一身，<caesura/>或因行坐臥，</l>
<lb n="0476a11" ed="T"/><l>當獲人稱譽，<caesura/>壽命得時長，</l>
<lb n="0476a12" ed="T"/><l>人間受快樂。<caesura/>天龍及藥叉、</l>
<lb n="0476a13" ed="T"/><l>羅剎犍闥嚩、<caesura/>臭神食穢神、</l>
<lb n="0476a14" ed="T"/><l>惡心摩怛<note n="0476005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚕＝魯【元】【明】</note><note n="0476005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚕【大】，魯【元】【明】</note><app n="0476005"><lem wit="【大】">嚕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">魯</rdg></app>、<caesura/>女魅拏<note n="0476006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">明＝枳【三】</note><note n="0476006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">明【大】，枳【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0476006"><lem wit="【大】">明</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">枳</rdg></app>努、</l>
<lb n="0476a15" ed="T"/><l>塢娑怛羅等，<caesura/>癲癎及膊行、</l>
<lb n="0476a16" ed="T"/><l>吠怛拏大鬼、<caesura/>拏枳儞等神，</l>
<lb n="0476a17" ed="T"/><l>及餘惡心者，<caesura/>不敢越其影，</l>
<lb n="0476a18" ed="T"/><l>何況鬪戰處。<caesura/>暴惡之有情、</l>
<lb n="0476a19" ed="T"/><l>禁呪及幻術，<caesura/>悉不能侵害。</l>
<lb n="0476a20" ed="T"/><l>自在有威德，<caesura/>子孫及財產，</l>
<lb n="0476a21" ed="T"/><l>增長無有量，<caesura/>獲宿命智通，</l>
<lb n="0476a22" ed="T"/><l>上族見皆喜，<caesura/>無礙大辯才，</l>
<lb n="0476a23" ed="T"/><l>了達諸論義。<caesura/>得遇善知識，</l>
<lb n="0476a24" ed="T"/><l>莊嚴菩提心，<caesura/>於生生世世，</l>
<lb n="0476a25" ed="T"/><l>恒親近諸佛。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0476a26" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>讚揚聖德多羅菩薩一百八名經</cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
